    "extras": [
      "Book Postojna Cave, Predjama and Skocjan Caves ahead in summer; cave tour times are fixed and the best slots sell first.",
      "For Bled and Bohinj, buses are usually easier than trains because they drop you closer to the lakefront; keep SŽ for longer city hops like Postojna-Maribor.",
      "Piran's old town is pedestrian-only, so pack light for the last stretch from the bus stop and expect some stone lanes and stairs.",
      "Most places take cards, but carry a little cash for market snacks, bus stations and small mountain or coastal kiosks."
    ],
